cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper is about fine-tuning pre-trained Transformer models for natural language tasks, specifically answer sentence selection in Question Answering. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which suggests cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also deals with information retrieval, which suggests cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the paper involves neural networks, which suggests cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
